quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,203,"JaŇčtee Innde Alla he √Īal…ói limtaa…ói. On yaccin…óo he nder bal…óe …ói…ói, bakkaatu fawaaki mo; on ne…ďtin…óo kadi, bakkaatu fawaaki mo.Wonande on deentii…óo . Hulee Alla, nganndon pellet …óo makko moo…ďindiroyte-…óon."
  2,204,"No he yim…ďe …ďee oon mo konngol makko haawat maa ka nguurdam aduna, himo seedna Alla ko woni he nder …ďernde makko, hara non ko kaŇčko …ďuri sa…ótude weejnde."
  2,205,"Si (So) o ruŇčtiima , o yaha ka leydi fii o bonna he mayri, o halka gese e ge√Ī√Īi (ge√Īli). Alla Yi…óaa bononnda."
  2,206,"Si o wi'aama: "Hulu Alla", mawnikinaare he…ďa mo sabu bakkaatu. Jahannama yonii mo, e nge bonii nda…ó…óudi!"
  2,207,"No woodi he yim…ďe …ďee oon coodtotoo…óo wonki mun kii …óa…ď…ďugol yarluye Alla. Alla ko Hilnotoo…óo (kinnotoo…óo) jeyaa…ďe makko …ďen (…ďee)."
  2,208,"Heey mon gom…óim…ďe, naatee he kisal denndanngal, wata on jokku juri (taa…ďe) seytaane …óin (…óee). On ko ga√Īo moo…óon …ďaŇčngu…óo."
  2,209,"Si on oo√Īike …ďaawo ko ari on he …ďannginaa…óe (la…ď…ďinaa…óe), nganndee pellet, Alla ko foolu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo (√Īee√Ī…óu…óo)."
  2,210,"Mbele wonaa …ďe padi ko haa nde Alla (Geno) ari he ma…ď…ďe he nder ni…ď…ďe duule wondude e Maalaa'ika en; fiyaaku nguu √Īaawaama. ka (…óo) Alla woni ruttorde fiyakuuji …óin."